title: [Solhaven, South Market North]
description: A narrow storefront with a blue-shingled bay window occupies the center of the row of shops along this side of the market.  A variety of gadgets and navigational instruments fill the velvet lined display behind the window's many panes.

A storefront with a blue-shingled bay window occupies the center of the row of shops along this side of the market, a narrow lane tucked between it and the yellow-awninged shop to its east.  A variety of gadgets and navigational instruments fill the velvet lined display behind the window's many panes.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
